            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "” – I don’t really care which since they seem to go together so often these days when it comes to the never-ending quest for impeccable safety. Just like how road fatalities in the United States and other countries have actually increased as government mandates shove more “",
